title: Sell  Out or Loyal
itunes:title: Sell  Out or Loyal
description:
3-18- Today's episode we opened up the phone lines to see if any of our listeners are savages and would sell out a family member for money, after story broke about Jeff Bezo's girlfriend's brother sold their texts for $200k. Moreover, we also opened up the phone lines for our listeners to humble "The Breakfast Club" with our segment "Slander the Breakfast Club". Also, Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day" to Rich Dollaz for being to old to fight at the Love and Hip Hop Reunion.
